  <div class="c-entry-box--compact__body">
    
    
    
    <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="feature" href="https://www.theverge.com/2017/7/10/15938500/leica-tl2-mirrorless-camera-review">Leica’s new TL2 is a much improved mirrorless camera</a></h2>
    
      <p class="p-dek c-entry-box--compact__dek" data-chorus-optimize-field="dek">More resolution and much snappier performance make Leica’s entry-level camera much more appealing</p>
    
    
    
      
